00:02:21.190 --> 00:02:23.910
because very often,
we are not asking

00:02:23.910 --> 00:02:27.520
why did this behavior occur,
some human social behavior that

00:02:27.520 --> 00:02:31.810
is completely benign, but often
some fairly disastrous ones.

00:02:31.810 --> 00:02:33.880
Why did this behavior occur?

00:02:33.880 --> 00:02:36.600
Very often what is
between the lines

00:02:36.600 --> 00:02:39.280
