the temporal personality

00:25:24.730 --> 00:25:25.490
business.

00:25:25.490 --> 00:25:28.460
And again, that
challenge of, most of us

00:25:28.460 --> 00:25:30.410
have gotten to our
religious stances

00:25:30.410 --> 00:25:34.010
through a great deal of
hard work and introspection.

00:25:34.010 --> 00:25:37.590
And, even if only once in
the history of the universe,

00:25:37.590 --> 00:25:39.660
somebody instead
has gotten there

00:25:39.660 --> 00:25:42.780
because their neurons
have synchronized firing

00:25:42.780 --> 00:25:45.380
in their limbic systems
once every six months,

00:25:45.380 --> 00:25:49.270
that is very challenging to
the sense of no longer talking

00:25:49.270 --> 00:25:51.730
about them, and very
challenging to the sense

00:25:51.730 --> 00:25:56.370
of making sense of us as
autonomous individuals

00:25:56.370 --> 00:25:59.040
within our own control.

00:25:59.040 --> 00:26:00.590
Other realms of this.

00:26:00.590 --> 00:26:01.870
OCD.

00:26:01.870 --> 00:26:04.660
Again, we've got some sense,
