Here's what I've been wasting
most of today thinking about.

00:37:02.470 --> 00:37:04.259
I have a grant due
next week, and I'm

00:37:04.259 --> 00:37:05.800
getting so little
done on it that I'm

00:37:05.800 --> 00:37:06.841
beginning to get anxious.

00:37:06.841 --> 00:37:09.430
So I've been having
this whole repeated

00:37:09.430 --> 00:37:16.190
pattern of this intrusive force
thinking about, Charlie Bit Me.

